DTOs for the Standard BOM.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSourceArtifactRef
    One entry in the list of source artifacts.
    BomEntry
    Describes an entry in a standard-bom-compliant SBOM.
    CustomProperty
    The names of custom properties that we support in CycloneDX Components as per the Siemens Property Taxonomy for CycloneDX.
    ExternalComponent
    A component which is referenced by this SBOM, but which is not itself part of it.
    SourceArtifactRefLocal
    A source artifact reference which explicitly refers to a downloaded copy of the source archive via a relative path.
    SourceArtifactRefUrl
    A source artifact reference which explicitly refers to the original remote URL of the source archive.
    StandardBom
    Main DTO for the complete "Standard BOM" JSON structure.
